I'm seeing a similar issue with TF on native Windows 10 (TF 0.12) for dense_shape while running the wide_n_deep_tutorial shipped with the package. I pulled the latest version of TF as well but still didn't resolve the problem:

TypeError: init() got an unexpected keyword argument 'dense_shape'

Cannot comment whether this happens on Unix also. I've python 3.5.2 installed. Any ideas?
